  "details": "A vulnerability was detected in Totolink N300RT 3.4.0-B20250430. The impacted element is the function is_cmd_string_valid of the file /boafrm/formWsc of the component libapmib.so. Performing a manipulation of the argument localPin results in buffer overflow. The attack is possible to be carried out remotely. The exploit is now public and may be used.",
